metadata.name: Venus
metadata.description:
"I am tired, I am weary
I could sleep for a thousand years
A thousand dreams that would awake me
Different colors made of tears"

Inspired by the song Venus in Furs by The Velvet Underground, I wanted to do a surreal portrait that is reminiscent of the song. This was created by generating  several pieces in AI (Dream by WOMBO) and using SketchBook app to collage pieces and make hand-drawn edits.
